results.title: Intramuscular atenolol and levetiracetam reduce mortality in a rat model of paraoxon-induced status epilepticus.
results.text_hl: @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@AT@@@ + @CHEMICAL_Levetiracetam @CHEMICAL_MESH:D000077287 @@@LV@@@ therapy exhibited @<m>DISEASE_Muscle_Neoplasms</m> @DISEASE_MESH:D019042 @@@muscle pathology@@@ @DISEASE_Inflammation @DISEASE_MESH:D007249 @@@inflammation@@@ scores that were not significantly different from saline-treated controls.
